ts of religion in Western democracies; and the current controversies in genetic technology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aPolitical ethics. 0aPolitical sciencexPhilosophy. 0aSolidarity. 4aPhilosophy : Ethics. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Democracy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 4aSociology : Sociology. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Ethics & Moral Philosophy.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079147871440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791478714423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791478714/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles